OL,3,CTV-related anniversaries for 18 APR
OL,4,CTV TRANSMITTERS
OL,5,
OL,6,CG2012FIn the early hours of the
OL,7,Fmorning, the remaining analogue
OL,8,Fchannels (BBC One, ITV and Channel 4)
OL,9,Fare switched off at the Crystal Palace
OL,10,Ftransmitter.
OL,11,
OL,12,FWhen analogue Channel 4 transmissions
OL,13,Fceased, the ETP-1 test card was shown
OL,14,Ffor a short period, minus the
OL,15,Fblue/white channel ID, which would've
OL,16,Fincluded the old NTL branding.
OL,17,
OL,18,FEarlier in the month (4th April)
OL,19,Fanalogue BBC Two transmissions ceased.
OL,20,
OL,21,FLondon's terrestrial transmission
OL,22,Fsystem is now digital only.
